Class VehicleDAOImpl

java.lang.Object
com.algonquin.www.dao.AbstractGenericDAO
com.algonquin.www.dao.impl.VehicleDAOImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
VehicleDAO
public class VehicleDAOImpl extends AbstractGenericDAO implements VehicleDAO
Implementation of VehicleDAO for managing Vehicle entities in the database.

Provides CRUD operations such as adding, searching, and updating vehicle records using JDBC connections obtained from DataSource.
